<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Mountain Adventure</title>

  <style>
    body {
      background-color: skyblue;
      background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, skyblue, lightgreen);
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      background-position: top center;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    .header {
      background-image: linear-gradient(to right, teal, green);
      border-radius: 15px;
      text-align: center;
      color: white;
      padding: 15px;
    }

    .info-box {
      background-color: white;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 15px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      color: darkslategray;
    }

    .info-box h2 {
      color: forestgreen;
    }

    .sun {
      width: 60px;
      height: 60px;
      background-color: gold;
      border-radius: 50%;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      color: darkgreen;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>

</head>
<body>

  <div class="header">
    <h1>Mountain Adventure</h1>
    <p>Welcome to the world of mountains!</p>
  </div>

  <div class="info-box">
    <h2>Interesting Fact</h2>
    <p>Mount Everest is the highest mountain above sea level.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="sun"></div>

  <p class="footer">Created by ___________</p>

</body>
</html>
